50|$|Rear Admiral Makbul also {{performed}} {{the duties of}} COMCHIT, COMSWADS and Administrative Authority Dhaka. He has served as Principal of Marine Fisheries Academy, Director in NHQ and Director in DGFI and <b>Assistant</b> <b>Chief</b> <b>of</b> Naval <b>Staff</b> (Personnel). He served as Director General of Bangladesh Coast Guard. He is currently serving as <b>Assistant</b> <b>Chief</b> <b>of</b> Naval <b>Staff</b> (Operation).|$|R
